PrecisReappointment of SANDRA J. LEWIS-den OTTER, of Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory, Ontario, as a part-time member of the National Parole Board, Ontario Regional Division, to hold office during good behaviour for a period of three years, effective April 15, 1999.
